---
const title = "Méthode de Musique Moderne";
---

<html lang="fr">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>{title}</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="layout-container">
			<header class="hero">
				<h1>Quelle discipline voulez-vous maîtriser ?</h1>
				<p class="subtitle">Choisissez votre instrument et commencez votre apprentissage autonome dès aujourd'hui.</p>
			</header>

			<main class="instruments-grid">
				<!-- Carte Piano -->
				<a href="/methode-musique/piano" class="instrument-card piano">
					<div class="card-overlay"></div>
					<div class="card-content">
						<span class="emoji">🎹</span>
						<h2>Piano</h2>
						<p>Maîtrisez l'harmonie, les accords et l'indépendance mélodique.</p>
						<span class="start-link">Entrer dans le studio →</span>
					</div>
				</a>

				<!-- Carte Batterie -->
				<a href="/methode-musique/batterie" class="instrument-card batterie">
					<div class="card-overlay"></div>
					<div class="card-content">
						<span class="emoji">🥁</span>
						<h2>Batterie</h2>
						<p>Développez votre rythme, votre coordination physique et votre groove.</p>
						<span class="start-link">Entrer dans le studio →</span>
					</div>
				</a>
			</main>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	:root {
		--bg: #090d16;
		--text: #f8fafc;
		--text-muted: #94a3b8;
		--border: #1e293b;
	}

	* {
		box-sizing: border-box;
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
	}

	body {
		background-color: var(--bg);
		color: var(--text);
		font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
		min-height: 100vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.layout-container {
		max-width: 900px;
		width: 100%;
		padding: 40px 24px;
	}

	.hero {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 48px;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		letter-spacing: -0.025em;
		margin-bottom: 16px;
		background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffffff, #94a3b8);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
	}

	.subtitle {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.instruments-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		gap: 24px;
	}

	@media (min-width: 640px) {
		.instruments-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		}
	}

	.instrument-card {
		position: relative;
		background-color: #111827;
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 20px;
		padding: 40px 32px;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: var(--text);
		overflow: hidden;
		transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
	}

	.instrument-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px -10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
	}

	.instrument-card.piano:hover {
		border-color: #38bdf8;
	}

	.instrument-card.batterie:hover {
		border-color: #f59e0b;
	}

	.emoji {
		font-size: 3rem;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}

	h2 {
		font-size: 1.75rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 12px;
	}

	.instrument-card p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 32px;
		min-height: 48px;
	}

	.start-link {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}

	.piano .start-link { color: #38bdf8; }
	.batterie .start-link { color: #f59e0b; }

	.piano:hover .start-link { color: #0ea5e9; }
	.batterie:hover .start-link { color: #d97706; }
</style>